# Security

Read [SECURITY.md](../../SECURITY.md).

## Secrets

- Never commit `*.secrets.json`, `.env`, or API tokens
- Use `*.secrets.json.example` for templates
- Every execution path must call `loadSecrets` and pass `secrets` to `executeFlow`

## HTTP nodes

- Resolved URLs must be `http:` or `https:` only
- Reject `file:`, `ftp:`, and URLs without a host at execute time
- Quester does not sandbox egress — document in SECURITY.md, do not add silent blocks for localhost

## Desktop

- Validate flows in main process before execution
- Renderer must not execute HTTP directly — use RPC to main process

## In-code TODOs

Use `TODO(#issue)` referencing an open GitHub issue. No orphan TODOs.
